snippet.title: Tomb Raider AOD Flash Game (2004)
snippet.description: In this rare old flash game promoting the release of #TombRaider the Angel Of Darkness in Japan #LaraCroft collects coins, frogs, crystals and bananas avoiding bats, arrows and piranhas. Odd and kind of awkward
